tokens.name: Monaco
tokens.description:
The MCO project, formerly known as Monaco, started in June 2016 with the vision to put cryptocurrency in every wallet. On July 6th, 2018, Monaco announced its rebrand to CRYPTO.com and its consumer services (including MCO Visa Card and MCO Wallet App) have been rebranded as MCO. 

MCO is redefining how money is being moved, spent and invested. MCO is democratizing blockchain technology by designing beautiful, simple and useful financial services that have a lasting, positive impact on peopleâ€™s lives.
